---
title: Honey-Soy Chicken & Roast Veggie Salad with Japanese Mayo & Crushed Peanuts
description: The magic in this dish is the juicy chicken thigh, perfectly browned and then drizzled with our tasty Japanese mayo. Add a nourishing roasted salad and some crushed peanuts in the mix, and you've got an Asian-inspired meal in no time!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ftc-nz-asian-soy-chicken-thigh-salad-b37a4dbd.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/ftc-nz-asian-soy-chicken-thigh-salad-5f8d1ab42fc2d449276c5f2b-7c7067a9.pdf
